overview:
http://www.LunchMix.com - it is an online lunch dating service for busy professionals. LunchMix allows users to create a free profile, search for other single professionals close to work and set up a lunch date.

This platform provides its members with many advantages over mainstream dating sites; there is a higher likelihood of dates during the week, dating is no longer strictly a weekend and/or evening time commitment, and most importantly, members have an easy out if things are not going well on their lunchmix date. They can simply say “It was nice meeting you but I have to get back to work now”. No pressure and no hard feelings.

I have developed an iPhone app and facebook application for LunchMix as well.

iPhone App : http://itunes.apple.com/us/app/lunchmix.com-lunch-dating/id467039646?mt=8

LunchMix offers:

  1. An online dating system
  2. A mobile app
  3. A facebook application

LunchMix.com is a service that is owned and operated by JSC Networks, LLC.
